Two security guards are in a critical condition after being shot close to a railway line in City Deep in Johannesburg south in the early hours of Sunday paramedics said. Upon arrival at the scene paramedics found both men believed to be in their 30 s laying near the tracks said ER24 spokesperson Chitra Bodasing Harduth. During assessment it was found that the men were in a critical condition. They were treated and transported to hospital for further medical care she added.No further details were available.